<arggraph id="micro_c010" topic_id="older_people_better_parents" stance="pro">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[Older parents may make better parents.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[They may be more financially secure.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[They may have more patience]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[and be in a more secure relationship.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[One problem is they may not be as able to keep up with their kids or not be able to do as much fun stuff with them.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[But they can provide a more stable home.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e7"><![CDATA[They will be more able to make sure their kids have everything they need.]]></edu>
